Class BankRecords

  • java.lang.Object
    • iitbankpkg.BankRecords
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    iitbankpkg.Client

    public class BankRecords
extends java.lang.Object
implements iitbankpkg.Client
    Class Bank Records implements the interface Clients. 1.This class reads the data from a bank-Detail_withHeaders.csv file, 2.the data is manipulated using the getters/setters. 3.The console output shows first 25 records for various fields to the console via your getters. Records for the following fields: ID, AGE, SEX, REGION, INCOME, and MORTGAGE.Include headings in the print detail.
